reat that we're doing so many events now. What should I ask our fans about this time~...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Huh? Hey, that's... Eve-chan~! Over here!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Ah, Hina-san...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Fancy meeting you here. Are you on your way home?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Yes. It's nice to see you, Hina-san.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Hm? Are you okay? You seem kind of down.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Ah, is it because of when you got in trouble?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"The Talent Agency staff did give a pretty big lecture on the risks of getting too involved with our fans, didn't they~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"It makes sense that they would be angry... All I did was make the fighting worse.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"And from what I've seen it's still going on. Everyone's divided about whether all the cheering should be allowed or not.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"It's just like Chisato-san said. Looks like I just caused more problems.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"I'm worried about tomorrow's event. If this keeps up... will our fans... be able to enjoy themselves...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":20,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Don't worry about it! Everyone makes mistakes.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Hey, cheer up! Try shouting \"bushido~!\" You know, like you always do!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Uhm, o-okay. One... Two... B-bushido~...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Hm~, yeah, no energy at all. If the fans see this, they'll start to worry too.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"W-we can't have that. I don't want to concern our fans.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Then we'll just have to get your energy back! Now how are we going to do that~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Ah, how about heading to that one place?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"What one place...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Ryuseido! You said looking at the samurai armor there lifts your spirits, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"That's our best shot! Come on!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"oowarai01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"W-wait, Hina-san!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Sigh...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"So? Feeling better?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"I appreciate you taking me here, but... I'm sorry, I don't think it's going to happen today...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Usually gazing at this armor would do the trick, but nothing's changed. Haze surrounds my heart and it won't let up. I just feel so miserable...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Aww~, but why~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"...Uhh~, what are you guys up to?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":900000}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve & Hina","body":"Maya-san?!\nMaya-chan?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":17,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":900000,"voiceId":"event39-04-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"What are you doing here?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Ah, I saw the two of you earlier and it looked like Hina-san was taking you somewhere. I couldn't help but wonder what you guys were doing, so here I am.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Ahaha. Oh, okay.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Anyways, what's going on?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Eve-chan's feeling down, so I thought maybe coming here to look at this armor would cheer her up.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"It doesn't look like it worked though.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"I see. I think I see the problem here.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Eve-san's probably down because she's worried, right? In that case, wouldn't hearing her out do more than looking at armor?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Interesting~. Is that how that works?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"And I'm guessing you're worried about the fight that happened last time.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Yes, that's exactly it. Not only was I unable to stop an argument between our beloved fans, I also ended up making it worse.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":20,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Far from protecting everyone, I just caused more problems... I have no right to call myself a warrior...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Ah, you did mention wanting to protect everyone before, huh?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Still, I don't think you need to put so much of the blame on yourself...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"That's not the only thing, though. I'm also sad that I can't do anything for our fans.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Ah~, I get it. The staff did put a stop to everything after all.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Even if I could do something... I have no idea what that would be, seeing as I always mess everything up.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"What if I screw up again, and cause even more trouble? Pain and sorrow cloud my heart just from thinking about it...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Seems to me you've lost all confidence in yourself.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Well~, I know I'm one to talk, but... isn't what you want to do the most important thing here?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Me...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-052","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Yeah. What do you want to do, Eve-san?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf_left01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-053","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"What do I want? ... I-I want everyone to get along!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-054","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"If there's anything I can do to make that happen, I'll do it!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-055","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Alright, if that's what you want to do, let's do it. If we talk to the staff and Chisato-san, I'm sure they'll understand.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-056","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Huh? But... I'm not sure I can do this...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-057","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"You'll never know unless you try. Besides, I'll be there to help. If you think it's the right thing to do, I'll stand by your side.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-058","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"Hina","body":"Don't forget about me! Commence Operation: Make Our Fans Get Along!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event39-04-059","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"Maya-san, Hina-san... Thank you so much!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-060","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"Eve","body":"This time I will hold uphold my bushido way!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event39-04-061","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Fufu, that's the spirit. Looks like you're finally back to your normal cheerful self.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event39-04-062","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},